(5275, 1, '2018-05-15 11:10:34', '2018-05-15 05:40:34', '<b>Job Summary</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Job Description for Sr. Frontend Developer</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>An Android Developer who possesses a passion for pushing mobile technologies to the limits. You will work with our team of talented engineers to design and build the next generation of our mobile applications.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ensure the best possible performance, quality, and responsiveness of the application.</li>\r\n 	<li>Identify and correct bottlenecks and fix bugs.</li>\r\n 	<li>Design, build, and maintain high performance, reusable, and reliable Java code.</li>\r\n 	<li>Translate designs and wire-frames into high quality code.</li>\r\n 	<li>Design and build advanced applications for the Android platform.</li>\r\n 	<li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to define, design, and ship new features.</li>\r\n 	<li>Work with outside data sources and API''s.</li>\r\n 	<li>Unit-test code for robustness, including edge cases, usability, and general reliability.</li>\r\n 	<li>Continuously discover, evaluate, and implement new technologies to maximize development efficiency.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hands on experienced for Android Applications from scratch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lead modules and be responsible for timely delivery and software quality.</li>\r\n 	<li>Well versed with Web Services (SOAP or REST or JSON or XML)Skills: Android, Eclipse, JSON, Mobile Application Development, SQLite, Java J2EE, SDK, Android Studio, Android Application Development, Android NDK</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Technical skills required on Android:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><b>Mobile Application:</b> Android</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Web Applications :</b> HTML, JavaScript</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Databases :</b> SQLite, MySQL, SqlServer</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Programming Languages :</b> C, Java</li>\r\n 	<li><b>IDE :</b> Android Studio</li>\r\n 	<li><b>NOTIFICATIONS :</b> FCM, GCM</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Web Service Protocols</b> : REST</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Version Control tool:</b> Tortoise SVN</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>J.D. for PHP Developer</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The developer should have deep understanding and hand-on knowledge of Core PHP &amp; MySQL, XML/JSON and RDBMS concepts</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of web data mining (Web scraping, competitor monitoring, web crawling) and big data analytics projects.</li>\r\n 	<li>Write scalable, optimized and bug free code for web data mining projects test, debug, review, optimize and manage existing code written by other team members.</li>\r\n 	<li>Build reusable code and libraries for future use.</li>\r\n 	<li>Optimize PHP Code and MySQL queries for maximum speed and scalability.</li>\r\n 	<li>Collaborate with team members and keep them informed about project schedules and status.</li>\r\n 	<li>Work on different type of rest API</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Skills</b> - PHP, CSS, Java Script, jquery, Ajax, MySql, Code Igniter, Word Press, Angular JS\r\n\r\nCrowling, Scraping, Curl\r\n\r\n<b>Qualification -</b> Btech, BCA &amp; MCA\r\n\r\n<b>Experience</b> <b>for Team Lead / Tech Lead ( Android &amp; PHP )</b> - Minimum 4 Years\r\n\r\n<b>Salary -</b> Best of Industry', 'Front End Developer', '', 'expired', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'front-end-developer', '', '', '2018-06-15 02:54:55', '2018-06-14 21:24:55', '', 0, 'http://www.mobprodigital.com/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=5275', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0);
