(5448, 1, '2018-05-23 14:53:44', '2018-05-23 09:23:44', '<section class="container">\r\n        <div class="section-title">\r\n            <h2 class="widget-title">500+ Trusted Clients On The Board Who Have Achieved There Expected Results</h2>\r\n            <div class="seperator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="clear-both text-center"> The major issue Digital advertiser faces that the advertisement doesnâ€™t reaches to the right target audience. Here Mob Pro plays an important role by connecting the advertiser to the right traffic. Being the ad network Mob Pro try to help out the advertisers who have campaigns but are troubled as they are not reaching the right place. By associating with Mob Pro you will generate sales, leads, and visibility for your campaigns.</div>\r\n        <hr class="clear-both">\r\n    \r\n        <section class="clear-both overflow-auto">\r\n            <div class="section-title">\r\n                Features which make us popular\r\n            </div>\r\n            <article class="row">\r\n                <div class="col-sm">\r\n                    <div class="ad-icon">\r\n                        <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/help.png">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <h3 class="add-text">Help in generating effective leads</h3>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-sm">\r\n                    <div class="ad-icon">\r\n                        <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/smartphone.png">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <h3 class="add-text">App Installation</h3>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-sm">\r\n                    <div class="ad-icon">\r\n                        <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/happy.png">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <h3 class="add-text">Generating Impression for each visit</h3>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-sm">\r\n             