n Tool</h3>\r\n                <p class="article-info text-white">\r\n                    This tool will act as most important benefit while working with us. We help you detect if the clicks, installation, conversations, IP used is duplicate or original so that you can see that your campaigns is running successfully in the real time.\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="img-wrap text-center">\r\n                <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/fraud_detection_tool.png" alt="Fraud Detection Tool" />\r\n            </div>\r\n        </article>\r\n    <article class="article-section bg-white">\r\n            <div class="img-wrap text-center">\r\n                <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/customize_solution.png" alt="Customize Solutions" />\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="text-wrap">\r\n                <h3 class="article-title">Customize Solutions</h3>\r\n                <p class="article-info">\r\n                    The advertisers, who turn up to us, get the tailored services and assistance for their campaign as per their business demand.\r\n                </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </article>\r\n    </section>', 'Advertisers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5210-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-23 14:53:44', '2018-05-23 09:23:44', '', 5210, 'http://www.mobprodigital.com/5210-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(5449, 1, '2018-05-23 14:56:12', '2018-05-23 09:26:12', '<section class="container">\r\n    <p>A publisher is the counterpart of every successful running advertisement campaigns, as it provides the traffic which is the end user of the advertisement. Mob Pro facilitates the publisher with the high conversation rates, better payout, high monetization ratio.</p>\r\n    <p>Mob Pro benefits the publishers who are associated with them with them, so if you are on the list of becoming the publisher then itâ€™s time to get associated with us. We offer API/ S2S integration to clients in both the ways.</p>\r\n</section>    \r\n    <div class="inner-saparater">\r\n        Enjoy the perks while working with us as publisher\r\n    </div>\r\n    <article class="article-section bg-danger">\r\n        <div class="text-wrap">\r\n            <h3 class="article-title text-white">Easy Payments</h3>\r\n            <p class="article-info text-white"> We have simple logic that you give us traffic and we will convert them into monetary value. So, you donâ€™t have to worry that your payout will be delayed or you will not get the returns. </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="img-wrap text-center">\r\n            <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/easy_payment.png" alt="Easy Payments" />\r\n        </div>\r\n    </article>\r\n    <article class="article-section bg-white">\r\n        <div class="img-wrap text-center">\r\n            <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dedicated_managers.png" alt="Dedicated managers" />\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="text-wrap">\r\n            <h3 class="article-title">Dedicated managers</h3>\r\n            <p class="article-info">\r\n                The publisher working with us will get assistance 24/7 to make sure they get real-time updates. We work on to optimize the traffic so that publisher gets the best monetize return. We believe in keeping the clients, so our team will especially look into your requirement.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </article>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <article class="article-section bg-primary">\r\n    \r\n        <div class="text-wrap">\r\n            <h3 class="article-title text-white">Real-Time Reporting</h3>\r\n            <p class="article-info text-white">\r\n                We exclusively believe in that when a publisher has joined hand with us, look forward to knowing everything in real time.\r\n                We provide the dashboard where a publisher can see the happenings.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="img-wrap text-center">\r\n            <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/realtime_updates.png" alt="Real-Time Reporting" />\r\n        </div>\r\n    </article>\r\n    \r\n    <article class="article-section bg-white">\r\n    \r\n        <div class="img-wrap text-center">\r\n            <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tailored_reporting.png" alt="Tailored offer" />\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="text-wrap">\r\n            <h3 class="article-title">Tailored offer</h3>\r\n            <p class="article-info">\r\n                While working with us the publishers will get the various running campaigns according to their niche. We believe in tailored services, so you will get what you are looking at a profitable ratio.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </article>', 'Publishers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5220-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-23 14:56:12', '2018-05-23 09:26:12', '', 5220, 'http://www.mobprodigital.com/5220-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
