(5566, 1, '2018-05-25 12:07:03', '2018-05-25 06:37:03', '<section class="container">A publisher is the counterpart of every successful running advertisement campaigns, as it provides the traffic which is the end user of the advertisement. MobPro facilitates the publisher with the high conversation rates, better payout, high monetization ratio.MobPro benefits the publishers who are associated with them with them, so if you are on the list of becoming the publisher then itâ€™s time to get associated with us. We offer API/ S2S integration to clients in both the ways.</section>\r\n<div class="inner-saparater">Enjoy the perks while working with us as publisher</div>\r\n<article class="article-section bg-danger">\r\n<div class="text-wrap">\r\n<h3 class="article-title text-white">Easy Payments</h3>\r\n<p class="article-info text-white text-center">We have simple logic that you give us traffic and we will convert them into monetary value. So, you donâ€™t have to worry that your payout will be delayed or you will not get the returns.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="img-wrap text-center"><img alt="Easy Payments" src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/easy_payment.png"></div>\r\n</article><article class="article-section bg-white">\r\n<div class="img-wrap text-center"><img alt="Dedicated managers" src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/dedicated_managers.png"></div>\r\n<div class="text-wrap">\r\n<h3 class="article-title">Dedicated managers</h3>\r\n<p class="article-info text-center">The publisher working with us will get assistance 24/7 to make sure they get real-time updates. We work on to optimize the traffic so that publisher gets the best monetize return. We believe in keeping the clients, so our team will especially look into your requirement.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article class="article-section bg-primary">\r\n<div class="text-wrap">\r\n<h3 class="article-title text-white">Real-Time Reporting</h3>\r\n<p class="article-info text-white text-center">We exclusively believe in that when a publisher has joined hand with us, look forward to knowing everything in real time.\r\nWe provide the dashboard where a publisher can see the happenings.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="img-wrap text-center"><img alt="Real-Time Reporting" src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/realtime_updates.png"></div>\r\n</article><article class="article-section bg-white">\r\n<div class="img-wrap text-center"><img alt="Tailored offer" src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tailored_reporting.png"></div>\r\n<div class="text-wrap">\r\n<h3 class="article-title">Tailored offer</h3>\r\n<p class="article-info text-center">While working with us the publishers will get the various running campaigns according to their niche. We believe in tailored services, so you will get what you are looking at a profitable ratio.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article>', 'Publishers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5220-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-25 12:07:03', '2018-05-25 06:37:03', '', 5220, 'http://www.mobprodigital.com/5220-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(5567, 1, '2018-05-25 12:10:23', '2018-05-25 06:40:23', '<section class="container">\r\n<div class="section-title">\r\n<h2 class="widget-title">500+ Trusted Clients On The Board Who Have Achieved There Expected Results</h2>\r\n<div class="seperator">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear-both text-center">The major issue Digital advertiser faces that the advertisement doesnâ€™t reaches to the right target audience. Here MobPro plays an important role by connecting the advertiser to the right traffic. Being the ad network MobPro try to help out the advertisers who have campaigns but are troubled as they are not reaching the right place. By associating with MobPro you will generate sales, leads, and visibility for your campaigns.&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<hr class="clear-both">\r\n\r\n<section class="clear-both overflow-auto">\r\n<div class="section-title">Features which make us popular</div>\r\n<article class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm">\r\n<div class="ad-icon"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/help.png"></div>\r\n<h3 class="add-text">Help in generating effective leads</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm">\r\n<div class="ad-icon"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/smartphone.png"></div>\r\n<h3 class="add-text">App Installation</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm">\r\n<div class="ad-icon"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/happy.png"></div>\r\n<h3 class="add-text">Generating Impression for each visit</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm">\r\n<div class="ad-icon"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/api.png"></div>\r\n<h3 class="add-text">Access of API/S2S in both ways</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</article></section></section><!-- container end -->\r\n<div class="inner-saparater">Benefits which advertiser will grasp by associating while working with MobPro</div>\r\n<section><article class="article-section bg-info">\r\n<div class="text-wrap">\r\n<h3 class="article-title text-white">Dedicated Specialist</h3>\r\n<p class="article-info text-white text-center">MobPro ha